              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25309847/" class="">第325页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54704732/" class=" " title="剥洋葱">剥洋葱</a>
                (梦里彩云疑冉冉，愁边春水故粼粼)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25309847">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">这一比较不伦不类。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-22 14:59</span>
                  
